OL,4,CBBC over-75s free TV licence transition
OL,5,Cperiod to end in July
OL,6, The BBC will end its licence fee grace
OL,7, period for over-75s on 31 July, with
OL,8, 260,000 pensioners still yet to pay.
OL,10,FThe right to a free TV licence for that
OL,11,Fage group ended last August for all
OL,12,Fexcept those in receipt of the pension
OL,13,Fcredit benefit.
OL,15,FBut in February, the BBC announced a
OL,16,Ftransition period due to the pandemic.
OL,18,FThe BBC said that, of the 3.9 million
OL,19,Fpeople over 75 who needed to make new
OL,20,FTV licence arrangements, 3.6 million
OL,21,Fhad now done so.
